15 (4) "Podiatric residency" means a program of supervised postgraduate clinical
16 training approved by the board for a licensed podiatric resident;
17 (5) "Podiatric resident" means a person licensed by the board and participating in a
18 podiatric residency;
19 (6) "Podiatric supervision" has the same meaning as in Section 10 of this Act;
