21 podiatric medicine accredited by the Council on Podiatric Medical[Podiatry]
22 Education of the American Podiatric Medical[Podiatry] Association or approved
23 by state licensing boards;
24 (8) "Podiatry" is that profession of the health sciences which deals with the
25 examination, diagnosis, treatment, and prevention of diseases, conditions, and
